<Layout>

    <div class="text-container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>
<br>
Effective Date: June 19, 2026
<br>
Last Updated: June 19, 2026
<br><br>
This Privacy Policy explains how this portfolio website handles information. I value your privacy and believe in maintaining full transparency regarding the technical architecture of this platform and any minimal data processing that may occur.
<br><br>
<strong>1. Executive Summary</strong>
<br>
This Site is designed as a static portfolio built using modern client-side technologies (Astro, Three.js, and Bootstrap) and is hosted on Netlify.
<br>
I do not collect, store, or sell any personal data. No user accounts are required, there are no contact forms storing database records on this domain, and no marketing trackers are utilized. The only utility used to monitor aggregate, non-identifiable usage is Umami Analytics.
<br><br>
2. Analytics (Umami)
<br>
To understand general visitor traffic and improve the performance of this Site, I use Umami, a privacy-focused, open-source analytics platform.

Unlike traditional tracking suites, Umami is designed to respect your right to privacy:
<br>
No Cookies: Umami does not write any cookies or local storage data to your browser.
<br>
No Personal Data Collection: It does not track you across different websites.
<br>
Anonymization: All visitor IP addresses are fully anonymized.
<br>
GDPR Compliance: The tracking is completely anonymous, requiring no consent banners under European GDPR regulations since no personally identifiable information (PII) is processed.
<br>
The data collected is restricted to basic metrics such as page views, device types, operating systems, and geographic regions (country level only).
<br><br>
3. Infrastructure and Hosting (Netlify)
<br>
This Site is hosted and distributed globally via Netlify.
<br>
When you access any website hosted on Netlify, their servers automatically record standard technical connection details. This may include:
<br>
Your IP address (temporarily processed for security and network delivery purposes).
<br>
Browser user-agent string.
<br>
Date and time of the request.
<br>
This data is processed solely by Netlify to ensure the security, integrity, and performance of their Content Delivery Network (CDN) and is handled in compliance with Netlify's own Privacy Policy. I do not store, access, or harvest these server logs for personal use.
<br><br>
4. Client-Side Rendering
<br>
This Site utilizes Three.js for interactive 3D graphics and Bootstrap for responsive layout styling.
<br>
All 3D rendering and visual calculations are performed strictly locally on your device (using your GPU/CPU via WebGL).
<br>
No data concerning your hardware capabilities, interaction coordinates, or performance telemetry is transmitted to any external server.
<br><br>
5. Third-Party Links
<br>
The Site contains links to external web resources (e.g., GitHub, LinkedIn, or external project links). Please be aware that once you leave this domain, you are subject to the privacy policies of those respective third-party platforms.
<br><br>
6. Your Rights
<br>
Because I do not collect, store, or process any of your personal data on this Site, there is no personal information to access, rectify, port, or erase.
<br><br>
7. Contact Information
